// Get Started — single multi-step Vibe Code block on /get-started.
// Steps: Team → Personalize → Plan → Checkout. One Softr page, internal step state.
//
// SOFTR CONFIG REQUIRED:
//   Source tab: bind to USERS table (database "brieflee beta"), filter to logged-in user.
//   Actions tab: auto-populated from q.select aliases below — Bev only needs to confirm
//                visibility/permissions for the update action.
//
// Cross-table caveat: the team step writes to ACCOUNTS (account name + team_emails),
// which a USERS-bound block can't do via useRecordUpdate. Until a Softr workflow exists
// to handle that, the team save is stubbed — data is collected, save is a no-op, the
// user advances. Plug TEAM_UPDATE_WORKFLOW_URL into a workflow that takes
// { accountId, teamName, teamEmails } and writes to accounts.name + accounts.team_emails.

